Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐　少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:07.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:30.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}逃げろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私を置いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}逃げろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}できません
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐を連れて逃げます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は　いい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}逃げません
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐が残るならば　ここで戦います
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}逃げると言うなら　少佐を連れて逃げます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:54.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶対　絶対　少佐を死なせません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:01:59.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう　やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:23.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は生きて　自由になりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あ　い…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「あい」って何ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「あい」って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かり　ません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:03.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私　分かりません　少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここだと思ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ひどい戦闘だった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君たちが信号弾を上げたあと　全員が突撃し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}負けを悟ったガルダリク軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:11.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撤退する前に　自らの総本部を砲撃した
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は　その階段の下で見つかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐らく　あいつは砲撃の瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君を守ろうと　突き飛ばしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入院している間　どなたに伺っても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐はご無事だと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言えなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:39.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は自分のことより　あいつの身ばかりを案じていて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこに…　行くのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:03.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は　少佐のいらっしゃる所にしか行けません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会社に戻るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君はうちの　自動手記人形だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　俺も　ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君が一緒に戻ってくれるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺はあいつに　君を託されたんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決戦開始の直前　あいつは俺の所へ来て言ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もし　私に何かあったら　ヴァイオレットを頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:45.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争が終結したら　ライデンのエヴァーガーデン家まで　あの子を送り届けてやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつは　決して君を戦う道具とは思っていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}１人の女の子としての　君の将来を案じていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}引っ張って悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:39.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}退院したばかりの頃は　どうなることかと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は　ちゃんとドールの仕事をこなせるようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当に頑張ったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつの命令がなくても　生きていけるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう　少佐に命令は頂けないのでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この話は　また今度にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}道が封鎖されてる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあいい　休め
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何かあったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ケスクレールの町が　ガルタリクの和平反対派に襲撃を受けました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反対勢力が活発化しているとは聞いていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}状況は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:44.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}制圧しましたが　まだ周辺の警戒を解ける状態ではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別の道を行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　戻ってきたんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}みたいだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仕事にも戻ってきますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと様子見てきてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前が行けばいいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんたくらいが　ちょうどいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:32.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「くらい」って何だよ　こっちはそれどころじゃねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ベネディクト　１２区辺りを捜してみてくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わしは１４区のほうへ行ってみる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何かあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:48.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新人の配達員が　配達しきれなかった手紙を捨ててしまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これから捜しに行くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫　大体あたりはついてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　いるんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すこしでいいから　顔を見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご心配おかけして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:31.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}体の具合はどう　ちゃんと食べてる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差し入れ置いとくわね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明日は　顔出せそう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}みんな待ってるし　あなたへの依頼もたくさん来てるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズ社長がおっしゃったとおり　燃えているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分がしてきたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか　俺が言ったことが分かる時が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:10.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして初めて　自分がたくさんヤケドしていることに気づくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしてそんなこと言ったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:22.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子の境遇を考えたら　しかたのないことだったじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}境遇が　どうであれ　経緯や理由が何であれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}してきたことは消せない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だったら忘れて　一からまた…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘れることもできないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えているのは　あの子だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺や君だって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}表面上は消えたように見えるヤケドの痕も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ずっと残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だったら　どうすればいいの　あの子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうするかは　自分で決めるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:00.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃え上がった体と向き合って　受け入れたあとに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:08.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子　少佐も　何もかもなくしてしまったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なくしてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カトレアさんも戻ってこない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明日は私が　あの子の様子見に行ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しばらく　そっとしておいてあげたほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「愛してる」を知りたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は少佐の「愛してる」が知りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ドールになったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当に　そっとしておくだけでいいんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このまま　あの子　もうドール辞めちゃうんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆を頼みたいんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご無事だったのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その服は？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:09.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今　私は自動手記人形として働いているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　手紙を代筆しております
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多くの命を奪った　その手で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人を結ぶ手紙を書くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐　少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は　どうしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令をください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前さん宛てだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリカとアイリスから頼まれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　確かに届けたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ　配達を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　捨てられた手紙が見つかったんでね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ベネディクトさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつ　足くじいてな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんな靴　履いてるからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まったく何やってんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イテテ…　痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　わしはクラフト通りを回るから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんたは　１本裏手を頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どれ１つ取ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰かの大切な思いだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}届かなくていい手紙なんてないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん　お父さんからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}配達　終わったかい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れさん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった　みんなちゃんと届いたんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ヴァイオレット　大丈夫」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「会いに行こうと思ったけど」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「アイリスと相談して手紙を書くことにしました」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ドールがドールに手紙を書くなんて　変かもしれないけれど」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:13.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「でも　伝えたかったの　心配してるって」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「それから　あなたのこと」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「待ってるって」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:26.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「今は　とても仕事に戻る気持ちにはなれないかもしれないから」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ゆっくり休んで」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「でも　何かあったら」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「遠慮なく私たちを呼んで」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:37.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「私も　アイリスも　あなたが戻ってくるのを信じてる」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:48.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「それから　今日　スペンサーさんって人があなたに代筆を頼みたいって来たわよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「妹さんに感謝とおわびの手紙を書きたいんですって」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「あなたに書いてほしいそうよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「どうしても　あなたじゃなきゃダメなんだって」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こちらで　よろしいでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:25.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妹に手紙を書くなんて　何か照れくさいが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:30.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも　あいつのおかげで　仕事も決まった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう一度　やり直す気持ちになれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悪かったな　わざわざ来てもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しばらく休むと聞いていたんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:49.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同僚が知らせてくれたのです　手紙で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは　私が生まれて初めてもらった手紙です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙をもらうというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とても　うれしいことなのだと分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ルクリアも喜ぶと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その名に　ふさわしい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その名が似合う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:21:59.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:13.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長の　おっしゃるとおり　私は　たくさんのヤケドをしていました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:24.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は自動手記人形でいていいのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて　生きていて　いいのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}してきたことは消せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:50.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:24.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君が自動手記人形としてやってきたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:34.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消えないんだよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:07.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:30.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要带少佐一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果少佐留在这里 我就在这里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要走的话 我就带着少佐一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:54.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我绝对 绝对不会让少佐死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:01:59.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:23.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你要活下去 自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真心地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「爱」是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「爱」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:03.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不懂 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我就猜你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是场残酷的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们发出信号弹后 我们全体突击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}败局已定的加达里克军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:11.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在撤退前 对自己的总部发起了炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你是在那段楼梯下被找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}恐怕是他在炮击的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了保护你 把你推开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}住院期间 不管我问谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都告诉我少佐没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:39.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你比起自己 更在乎他的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:03.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我只能去少佐的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}回公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你不是我们的自动手记人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我也呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等你和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}毕竟那家伙把你托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}临近决战前 他过来对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}万一我出了事 薇尔莉特就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:45.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}战争结束后 把她送去莱顿的伊芙加登家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那家伙从没有把你当成打仗的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而是把你当成一个女孩 替你的将来着想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉不该拽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:39.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你刚出院的时候 我还很不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你已经掌握了人偶的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算没有他的命令 应该也能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我再也收不到少佐的命令了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这事我们下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}路被封了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已经退…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}算了 稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}凯斯克莱尔城遭到加达里克的反和平势力袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之前就听说反对势力很活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:44.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然已经镇压住了 但还不能放松对周边的警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}走别的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特已经回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}会回来工作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去看看她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你去不就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这种人去正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:32.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么叫我这种人 我忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}贝内迪克特 你能去12区附近找找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去14区找找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:48.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}新人邮差把没送完的信丢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}正准备去找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没关系 大致的方向已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让我稍微看看你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让您担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:31.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}身体还好吧 有好好吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}慰问品我放门口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明天你能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家都在等你 还来了很多委托指名要你写
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}霍金斯社长说得对 我在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为自己做过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总有一天 你会明白我所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:10.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后才意识到自己早已烧到遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你为什么这么说她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:22.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想想她的遭遇 这些都是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不管遭遇如何 不管什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}做过的事不会因此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就忘了这些 从零开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也忘不掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}燃烧着的人 不只有她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}表面看似已经消失的烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也仍未痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那她到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}该怎么办 只能由她自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:00.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等她敢于正视自己燃烧的躯体 接受了事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:08.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她失去了少佐 失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她没有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嘉德丽雅小姐也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我明天去看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是暂时让她一个人静静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想知道「爱」是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想知道少佐的「我爱你」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才成为人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的应该让她一个人静静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再这样下去 她会不会不当人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想委托写信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这身衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:09.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我现在在当自动手记人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是 我在帮人代写书信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用你那夺走了众多性命的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去写为人们结缘的书信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请给我命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有封信给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是寄给你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}埃丽卡和爱丽丝拜托我送给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么信件已送达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还要继续送信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错 被丢掉的信都找回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}贝内迪克特先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那家伙扭到脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谁叫他穿那种鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是的 你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}疼疼疼…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我就去克拉夫特街送信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你去送后面那一条街
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}每一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都是人们重要的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在无需送达的书信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}妈妈 爸爸来信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}送完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了 信都送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原本打算来看看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但和爱丽丝商量后决定给你写信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然人偶给人偶写信可能有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:13.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我们想告诉你 我们很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 我们也在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:26.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也许你现在的心态还无法回来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 如果有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别客气 来找我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:37.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和爱丽丝都坚信你会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:48.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有 今天有位叫斯宾塞的先生来托你写信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说是想写信向妹妹表达感谢和歉意来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他说想让你来写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无论如何 非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样您看可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:25.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然写信给妹妹有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:30.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是多亏了她 我找到了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才决定从头开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉啊 还辛苦你专程过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我听说你最近在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:49.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是同事写信告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是我生平第一次收到信件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我现在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}收到信件 是件非常开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想露库莉娅也会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与这名字相称
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人如其名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:21:59.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:13.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}正如社长所言 我已被烧得遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:24.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真的可以继续当自动手记人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真的可以 活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}曾经的所作所为无法被抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:50.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:24.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你作为自动手记人偶所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:34.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也不会被抹去
